'''摩洛抵抗和解放组织'''（{{lang-tl|Moro Resistance and Liberation Organisasyon}}，缩写为MRLO）是[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]的一个[[左翼|左翼]][[分离主义|分离主义]]武装组织。该组织活动于[[棉兰老岛|棉兰老岛]]，参与[[摩洛冲突|摩洛冲突]]。该组织是[[菲律宾民族民主阵线|菲律宾民族民主阵线]]的[[摩洛人|摩洛人]]分支。该组织一直公开谴责菲律宾政府在棉兰老岛的军事行动，指控[[菲律宾武装部队|政府军]]对摩洛平民实施暴力行为<ref>{{cite news|last1=AYROSO|first1=DEE|title=Revolutionary Moro group calls for intensified armed struggle|url=http://bulatlat.com/main/2015/06/25/revolutionary-moro-group-calls-for-intensified-armed-struggle/|accessdate=29 June 2015|agency=Bulatlat.com#sthash.OtUynEX8.dpuf|date=June 25, 2015|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627230728/http://bulatlat.com/main/2015/06/25/revolutionary-moro-group-calls-for-intensified-armed-struggle/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.trackingterrorism.org/group/moro-resistance-liberation-organization-mrlo|title=Moro Resistance Liberation Organization (MRLO) {{!}} Terrorist Groups {{!}} TRAC|website=www.trackingterrorism.org|access-date=2019-06-05|archive-date=2018-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180223110913/https://www.trackingterrorism.org/group/moro-resistance-liberation-organization-mrlo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

